{"tid":1473970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企人攻略！唔知點同屋企人相處可以睇下！","createTime":"2019-08-15T04:09:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T05:02:34.000Z","uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fa1c7fb03fac3ba28c033e76ce330c7bd3f4d414","tid":1473970,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:09:53.000Z","msg":"單純係一個整合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鐘意就正皮推<br />\n<br />\n屋企人攻略，唔好爭執！！<br />\n用軟攻！！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">勾起對方情緒</span></strong></span>！！<br />\n其實嗰啲人冇同理心同情心<br />\n甚至冇學識所以講極唔明<br />\n你要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>對症下藥</strong></span></span><br />\n佢care 啲咩你針落去<br />\n錢？權？穩定？<br />\n例如新疆教育營，法輪功恐怖新聞？<br />\n支那通過送中後經濟必塌？<br />\n信用評分系統變低賤階層？<br />\n最緊要<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重覆</span></span></strong>洗返佢哋腦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>策略</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n藍絲攻略 - 拆解 18 種建制<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%97%8D%E7%B5%B2%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5-%E6%8B%86%E8%A7%A3-18-%E7%A8%AE%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%2597%258D%25E7%25B5%25B2%25E6%2594%25BB%25E7%2595%25A5-%25E6%258B%2586%25E8%25A7%25A3-18-%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2588%25B6%2F&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg4oeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=4cd02a65\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%2597%258D%25E7%25B5%25B2%25E6%2594%25BB%25E7%2595%25A5-%25E6%258B%2586%25E8%25A7%25A3-18-%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2588%25B6%2F&h=d6f310a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%97%8D%E7%B5%B2%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5-%E6%8B%86%E8%A7%A3-18-%E7%A8%AE%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6/</a><br />\n<br />\n其實藍絲好純真，要佢哋支持可能比想像中